---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/Container.astro";
import BackToPrevious from "@components/BackToPrevious.astro";
import { SITE } from "@consts";
---

<Layout title="About Us" description={SITE.DESCRIPTION}>
  <Container>
    <section class="animate space-y-10">
    <h1 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">
      About Us
    </h1>
    <article>
    <p>Welcome to Shopperqueries, your number one source for all things related to men's products. We're dedicated to giving you the very best of men's products, with a focus on dependability,uniqueness and reliability.</p>
    <p>Founded in 2025 by Mo, Shopperqueries has come a long way from its beginnings in the Internet. When Mo first started out, his passion for blogging drove them to build this website so that Shopperqueries can offer you good article. We now serve customers all over the world, and are thrilled that we're able to turn our passion into our own website.</p>
    <p>We hope you enjoy our products as much as we enjoy offering them to you. If you have any questions or comments, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
    <p>Mo</p>
    </article>
    </section>
  </Container>
</Layout>
